Class MapSize

java.lang.Object
org.tensorflow.op.RawOp
org.tensorflow.op.core.MapSize
All Implemented Interfaces:
Shaped, Op, Operand<TInt32>
@Operator public final class MapSize extends RawOp implements Operand<TInt32>
Op returns the number of elements in the underlying container.

    • asOutput

      public Output<TInt32> asOutput()
      Description copied from interface: Operand
      Returns the symbolic handle of the tensor.

      Inputs to TensorFlow operations are outputs of another TensorFlow operation. This method is used to obtain a symbolic handle that represents the computation of the input.

      Specified by:
      asOutput in interface Operand<TInt32>
